The layout of the source directory is as follows:

$(topsrcdir)/src/lib    - all c++ code and specific swig wrappers
$(topsrcdir)/src/fpga   - fpga code development
$(topsrcdir)/src/python - python code
$(topsrcdir)/src/patch  - patches that are applied to the gnuradio source tree
$(topsrcdir)/src/swig   - top level swig code to aggregate swig wrappers
$(topsrcdir)/src/util   - miscellaneous utilities

DEPRICATED CODE:
$(topsrcdir)/src/examples - depricated directory contains old examples which are
                            no longer supported and may not work anymore
